title: Oceania week problem
body: My Account name was not put on the artificial reef when i had over 10 points and My name was not offensive, can anyone tell my why or is it just a stuff up at riot ? also has this happened to anyone else but me ?

replies.body: wasn't the 2015 oceanic week the attack on the citys ?

Hey there,

Over 10 points? Sounds like you're talking about the most recent ocean week, the points earned during the 2016 ocean week will be going towards the Ocean Week community wall (More details coming in the near future).

The Nautilus Reef was for ocean week 2015, which is not the most recent. You only had to earn 3 points during the 2015 ocean week for your name to be on the reef.

You can find more information in [this thread](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/miscellaneous/LuyUu4E2-notice-nautilus-reef-and-you).
